      <name>Vitaliy-R</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/183</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;It looks like CLI command has changed since the recording of that video, and should include `config` like in&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@sap/datasphere-cli#from-the-command-line:" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://www.npmjs.com/package/@sap/datasphere-cli#from-the-command-line:&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;pre class="lia-code-sample language-bash"&gt;&lt;code&gt;datasphere config cache init -H https://mytenant.eu10.hcs.cloud.sap/ -p somepasscode&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;P&gt;Regards.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/datasphere-cli-not-working/qaa-p/14095304#M4913077"/>
