    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/community-corner-blog-posts/connect-with-sap-community-at-sap-sapphire-and-share-your-special-sap-event/bc-p/14101800#M146</id>
    <title>Re: Connect with SAP Community at SAP Sapphire and Share Your Special SAP Event Moment!</title>
    <updated>2025-05-15T01:04:43.134000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Vitaliy-R</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/183</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;There were many moments for me, starting from my very first presentation at the Community Day of SAP TechEd in 2007. Here with one of the biggest BW influencers for me -- Jens Doerpmund:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="VitaliyR_0-1747258359279.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/261236iDD0765A4B2984111/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="VitaliyR_0-1747258359279.png" alt="VitaliyR_0-1747258359279.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Then there were all the SAP Mentor magic moments, including &lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/additional-blog-posts-by-members/announcing-the-2010-scnotties-nominations/ba-p/12908723" target="_self"&gt;SCNotties Awards&lt;/A&gt;, or #HugTheSuit , or simply being freaking amazing:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="qualityisnotnrone.jpg" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/261249iA7B0889BC7815EE6/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="qualityisnotnrone.jpg" alt="qualityisnotnrone.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;We had a lot of fun coding during SAP InnoJams &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":nerd_face:"&gt;🤓&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;div class="video-embed-center video-embed"&gt;&lt;iframe class="embedly-embed" src="https://cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FqZUaHuybX9o%3Ffeature%3Doembed&amp;amp;display_name=YouTube&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqZUaHuybX9o&amp;amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FqZUaHuybX9o%2Fhqdefault.jpg&amp;amp;type=text%2Fhtml&amp;amp;schema=youtube" width="200" height="112" scrolling="no" title="SAP InnoJam Promo" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;" allowfullscreen="true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;And then, discussing the great community moment, I would like to bring my "baby": our &lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/wroclaw/gh-p/wroclaw" target="_self"&gt;SAP Community meetups in Wrocław&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":poland:"&gt;🇵🇱&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;div class="video-embed-center video-embed"&gt;&lt;iframe class="embedly-embed" src="https://cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FtF84GY1G_Bg%3Ffeature%3Doembed&amp;amp;display_name=YouTube&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtF84GY1G_Bg&amp;amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FtF84GY1G_Bg%2Fhqdefault.jpg&amp;amp;type=text%2Fhtml&amp;amp;schema=youtube" width="400" height="225" scrolling="no" title="Wrocław SAP Meetup 2015-2020: 5 years in pictures" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;" allowfullscreen="true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Let me call (in no particular order)&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/9840"&gt;@Ewelina&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to share their community moments from Katowice,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/312"&gt;@vladimirs_semikins&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;from Riga,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/8001"&gt;@Bartek&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;from Warszawa,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1515971"&gt;@Keti_Aladashvili&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;from Tbilisi,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/5396"&gt;@Tsovinar&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;from Yerevan, &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/833469"&gt;@justbraz&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;from Vilnius!&lt;/P&gt;</content>
